        {
            "title": "ADR低水426點  滙控阿里成元兇   兩電李寧靠穩",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恆指周五收市低426點或1.69%，報24851點，跌破25000關。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-172016__source-web_滙控-HSBC-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報120.55元，較香港收市價低3.2%，影響恒指60點 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合港幣119.85元，較香港收市價低3.1%，影響恒指58點 ;騰訊(00700)ADR折合港元計收報497.39元，較香港收市價低2.1%﹐跌破500關，影響恒指42點; 友邦保險(01299)ADR收市折合港幣83.58元，較香港收市價低2.9%; 影響恒指41點，4股成跌市主力。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港交所(00388)ADR收市折合港幣385.69元，較香港收市價低2.6% ; 建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合港幣7.95元，較香港收市價低1.7% ; 工商銀行(01398)ADR收市折合港幣6.46元，較香港收市價低2.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中華煤氣(00003)ADR收市折合港幣6.52元，較香港收市價低11.2%，影響恒指14點 ; 藥明生物(02269)ADR收市折合港幣32.58元，較香港收市價低3.7% ; 新東方(09901)ADR收市折合港幣43.07元，較香港收市價跌3.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中電(00002)ADR收市折合港幣74.02元，較香港收市價高0.6% ; 電能(00006)ADR收市折合港幣62.08元，較香港收市價0.4% ; 李寧(02331)ADR收市折合港幣21.52元，較香港收市價高0.4% 。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指夜市期指收報24725點，跌525點，較昨日恒指收市25277點，低水552點，成交29686張。國指夜市期指收報8409點，較昨日國指收市低水165點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15771395-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4426%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e6%88%90%e5%85%83%e5%85%87-%e5%85%a9%e9%9b%bb%e6%9d%8e%e5%af%a7%e9%9d%a0%e7%a9%a9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/ADR-1_source-bp_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 13:22:21",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "環境局：主要燃油供應商均表示目前供應正常",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">環境及生態局在社交平台說，鑑於中東局勢，局方今個星期與本地主要車用燃油供應商會面，要求必須保持供應穩定，所有供應商均表示目前供應正常，並會繼續致力維持穩定供應。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/bplib_20260223-182337_2026預算案_公共財政_政府部門_環境局_環境及生態局_水牌_source-bp_-1024x684.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/bplib_20260223-182337_2026預算案_公共財政_政府部門_環境局_環境及生態局_水牌_source-bp_-1024x684.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">因應社會關注車用油價升幅，局方引述供應商說，相對於大幅急升的國際成品油價格和其他地方車用燃油價的升幅，本地車用油價已屬於克制。局方提到，4月1日起，會每周公布各車用燃油供應商無鉛汽油和柴油折扣後零售價，以及國際成品油的市場指標價格走勢，有助公眾監察變化及了解相互關係。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">局方重申，政府會繼續密切留意地緣政治變化、國際能源價格走勢，及與各供應商密切監察本地燃油供應的情況，保障香港能源供應穩定。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15771116-%e7%92%b0%e5%a2%83%e5%b1%80%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e7%87%83%e6%b2%b9%e4%be%9b%e6%87%89%e5%95%86%e5%9d%87%e8%a1%a8%e7%a4%ba%e7%9b%ae%e5%89%8d%e4%be%9b%e6%87%89%e6%ad%a3%e5%b8%b8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20200413-CH-%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 13:05:57",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐股全線跌逾1%  英股失守萬點關   德股創近11個月新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲主要股市周五（3月20日）先升後跌，全線下挫超過1%，三大指數均錄得顯著跌幅，並創下近期新低。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國富時100指數收報9918點，跌145點或1.44%，自今年初以來首次失守一萬點大關。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">德國DAX指數表現最差，收報22380點，急挫459點或2.01%，創下近11個月收市新低。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">法國CAC指數收報7665點，跌142點或1.82%，亦創逾六個半月低位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">意大利富時MIB指數收報42840點，下挫1.97%或860點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報16714點，跌1.14%或191點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結本週表現，英法股市均累跌超過3%，德國股市更累跌約4.6%。三大指數均已連續第三個星期下跌，反映市場情緒持續疲弱。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15770473-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e5%85%a8%e7%b7%9a%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be1-%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e8%90%ac%e9%bb%9e%e9%97%9c-%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e5%89%b5%e8%bf%9111%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%8e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-1-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 12:57:15",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "布油高見113美元  全周飆9%五周連升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價持續急升，中東緊張局勢進一步升級，刺激油價向上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"油價\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"油價\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20200413-CH-oil_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">油價</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紐約期油4月合約走勢相對遜色，日內高位為99.67美元，未能突破100美元關口，收報98.32美元，升約2.3%。然而，本週累計轉跌0.4%，結束了此前連續4星期的升勢。<br/> <br/>   倫敦布蘭特期油5月合約連升4日，每桶一度高見113美元以上，最終收報112.19美元，單日升約3.3%。本週累計升幅更達約9%，實現連續5個星期上漲。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15770491-%e5%b8%83%e6%b2%b9%e9%ab%98%e8%a6%8b113%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83-%e5%85%a8%e5%91%a8%e9%a3%869%e4%ba%94%e5%91%a8%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/8a6d6fb35c89d9b0db4c4846f290c2c3_Iran_US_Oil_Prices_19824_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 12:57:16",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股道指挫1%納指插逾2%  一周計跌約2%連跌4周",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股尾市跌幅擴大，全日跌約1%至2%，連跌3日。道瓊斯工業平均指數與納斯達克指數技術上都跌至接近調整區，羅素2000指數成為2026年首個進入技術調整區的指數。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/c206d3ca9d54f9cb2c0548eb6bb639d0_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_87037_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/c206d3ca9d54f9cb2c0548eb6bb639d0_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_87037_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">周五為美股「四期結算日」(Quadruple witching day)，涉及合約金額約5.7萬億美元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美軍傳聞向中東增派兵力，投資者憂慮戰事加劇通脹，加息機會上升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯工業平均指數跌穿46000點水平收市，低開45點後，跌幅最多擴大至652點，低見45369點，收報45577點，跌443點，跌幅0.96%，創5個月收市新低。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">標普500指數與納指均創逾半年收市低位，標普指數收報6506點，跌100點，跌幅1.51%，曾挫2.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納斯達克指數收市失守22000點關口，收報21647點，跌443點，跌幅2.01%，一度滑落2.57%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數急挫2.92%，報6742點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">科技股沽壓顯著，Meta、Alphabet跌逾2%、Tesla、Nvidia跌3.2%。記憶體晶片股顯著下挫，美光、希捷科技、西部數據、SanDisk跌近5%至逾8%。另外，伺服器生產商超微電腦急瀉逾33.3%，美國指控超微電腦高層走私Nvidia晶片到中國。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">霍尼韋爾(Honeywell)股價下滑3.3%，為表現最差道指成份股，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">波音挫3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">個別金融股逆市靠穩，摩根士丹利升近2%，高盛升0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本周累計，美股連跌第4周，道指全周回吐2.1%，標指滑落1.9%，納指倒退2.1%，連跌4星期。金龍中國指數挫5.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15770541-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab1%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e6%8f%92%e9%80%be2-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88%e8%b7%8c%e7%b4%8425%e9%80%a3%e8%b7%8c4%e5%91%a8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240805_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 11:37:08",
